reviewText: Heaps of laughs with every movie. I don't know how many times I have seen BLAZING SADDLES and CADDYSHACK, but, I always have a belly full of laughs. Even VACATION and SPIES LIKE US have seen me watching them at least two times each. But, I actually never had a copy of any of them, only recorded copies from the tv and transferred to a home made dvd copy.....which no longer work properly. So, I was thrilled to be able to get all four in a set. Just make sure you empty the bladder before you start watching them.
Three out of four my favorite comedy movies!
Love the old movies tho to much sex stuff. I love funny tho I think reliaing on drugs, bad words and sex.
FOUR great movies in one  package
